    "attributes": {
        "action": "Legalise the use of passenger drones and 'mosquito helicopters'",
        "additional_details": "These aircraft can be more affordable and accessible than traditional helicopters, which could make aviation a reality for a broader segment of the population. Legalising these vehicles could encourage more people to become involved in aviation activities. Economic opportunities that these technologies could bring could also position the UK as a forward thinking nation that supports the growth of these types of vehicles, potentially attracting investment, talent and growth.",
        "background": "I want aviation regulations to be amended to legalise passenger drones and \u2018mosquito helicopters\u2019.",
